-- Sunoco posts Q1 loss on weak refining margins
-- 
-- Wed Apr 30, 2008 5:25pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/30/us-sunoco-results-idUSWNAS101220080430

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - U.S. refiner Sunoco Inc SUN.N posted a first-quarter loss on Wednesday from a year-earlier profit on weak margins for gasoline. 

 The company posted a net loss of $59 million, or 50 cents a share, compared with a profit of $175 million, or $1.44 a share, last year. Revenue rose to $12.81 billion from $9.31 billion last year. (Reporting by  Michael Erman )